<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="span12 profile-heading">
            <h2 class="pull-left">Domain verwalten</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="span12">
            <form novalidate name="domainForm" class="simple-form" ng-class="{clean: formclean, unclean: !formclean}">
                <tabset>
                    <tab active="tab1.active">
                        <tab-heading>Schritt 1</tab-heading>
                        <div class="tab-content-container" ng-form="step1form">
                            <h3>Domain [[ domain.name ]]<br>Standard-Banner-Konfiguration</h3>
                            <div class="horizontal-radio-group">
                                <dh-input
                                    type="radio"

                                    dh-name="forwardRadio"
                                    ng-model="formforwarding"
                                    dh-value="true"

                                    dh-label="Weiterleitung einrichten"
                                ></dh-input>
                                <dh-input
                                    type="radio"

                                    dh-name="forwardRadio"
                                    ng-model="formforwarding"
                                    dh-value="false"

                                    dh-label="keine Weiterleitung"
                                ></dh-input>
                                <div style="clear: both;"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div ng-show="formforwarding == 'true'">
                                <dh-input
                                    class="span6"
                                    type="url"

                                    dh-name="targetName"
                                    ng-model="banner.redirect_domain"

                                    dh-ng-required="formforwarding == 'true'"

                                    dh-label="Zieldomain eingeben"

                                    dh-tooltip="Bitte geben Sie eine gültige URL ein."
                                    dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                    dh-tooltip-placement="right"
                                    dh-tooltip-invalid="Bitte geben Sie eine gültige URL ein."
                                ></dh-input>
                            </div>
                            <label for="languages">In welcher Sprache soll der Banner angezeigt werden</label>
                            <dh-select class="span6" ng-model="banner.language" dh-options="languages"></dh-select>
                            <div class="tab-bottom-buttons">
                                <button style="visibility: hidden"><i class="icon-tick-left"></i>&nbsp;Schritt zurück</button>
                                <button>&nbsp;Vorschau ansehen</button>
                                <button class="pull-right next" ng-click="nextStep(step1form, tab2)"><i class="icon-tick-right icon-white pull-right"></i>Weiter&nbsp;</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </tab>
                    <tab active="tab2.active" disabled="!step1form.$valid">
                        <tab-heading>Schritt 2</tab-heading>
                        <div class="tab-content-container" ng-form="step2form">
                            <h3>Domain [[ domainName ]]<br>Standard-Banner-Konfiguration</h3>
                            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis scelerisque neque id viverra mollis. Sed mi sem, consequat eu ultrices non, imperdiet id tellus. Morbi et massa at elit tempus pellentesque nec ut eros. Vestibulum auctor enim eget aliquet porttitor. Nulla lacinia purus non elementum commodo.</p>
                            <dh-input
                                type="radio"

                                dh-name="positionRadio"
                                ng-model="banner.position"
                                dh-value="center"

                                dh-label="mittig"

                                dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                            ></dh-input>
                            <dh-input
                                type="radio"

                                dh-name="positionRadio"
                                ng-model="banner.position"
                                dh-value="top"

                                dh-label="oben"

                                dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                            ></dh-input>
                            <dh-input
                                type="radio"

                                dh-name="positionRadio"
                                ng-model="banner.position"
                                dh-value="right"

                                dh-label="rechts"

                                dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                            ></dh-input>
                            <dh-input
                                type="checkbox"

                                dh-name="secondvisitBox"
                                ng-model="formsecondvisit"
                                dh-value="true"

                                dh-label="ab dem 2. Besuch täglich soll ein anderer Banner angezeigt werden"

                                dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                            ></dh-input>
                            <div ng-show="formsecondvisit == true">
                                <dh-input
                                    type="radio"

                                    dh-name="secondpositionRadio"
                                    ng-model="banner.position_alternative"
                                    dh-value="top"

                                    dh-label="oben"

                                    dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                    dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                    dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                    dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                                ></dh-input>
                                <dh-input
                                    type="radio"

                                    dh-name="secondpositionRadio"
                                    ng-model="banner.position_alternative"
                                    dh-value="right"

                                    dh-label="rechts"

                                    dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                    dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                    dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                    dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                                ></dh-input>
                            </div>
                            <div class="tab-bottom-buttons">
                                <button ng-click="tab1.active = true"><i class="icon-tick-left"></i>&nbsp;Schritt zurück</button>
                                <button style="visibility: hidden">&nbsp;Vorschau ansehen</button>
                                <button class="pull-right next" ng-click="submit(tab3)"><i class="icon-tick-right icon-white pull-right"></i>Speichern&nbsp;</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </tab>
                    <tab active="tab3.active" disabled="!(step1form.$valid && step2form.$valid)">
                        <tab-heading>Finalisieren</tab-heading>
                        <div class="tab-content-container">
                            <h3>Die Einstellungen für [[ domainName ]] wurden erfolgreich gespeichert!</h3>
                            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis scelerisque neque id viverra mollis. Sed mi sem, consequat eu ultrices non, imperdiet id tellus. Morbi et massa at elit tempus pellentesque nec ut eros. Vestibulum auctor enim eget aliquet porttitor. Nulla lacinia purus non elementum commodo.</p>
                            <div class="row-fluid">
                                <div class="span4 offset2">
                                    <h4>Möglichkeit 1:<br>Aktivieren bei dotHIV</h4>
                                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis scelerisque neque id viverra mollis. Sed mi sem, consequat eu ultrices non, imperdiet id tellus.</p>
                                     <button>Jetzt aktivieren</button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="span4">
                                    <h4>Möglichkeit 2:<br>Code downloaden</h4>
                                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis scelerisque neque id viverra mollis. Sed mi sem, consequat eu ultrices non, imperdiet id tellus.</p>
                                     <button>Jetzt downloaden</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="tab-bottom-buttons">
                                    <button ng-click="tab2.active = true"><i class="icon-tick-left"></i>&nbsp;Schritt zurück</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </tab>
                </tabset>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
